+This repository is a fork which reworks the folder structure to contain only the official Arduino API and hardware‚Äëindependent code, in order to simplify Arduino API integration into STM32duino via a git submodule.
 
-* [megaavr](https://github.com/arduino/ArduinoCore-megaAVR)
